resourceMenu.keyboardInstructionsButtonAriaLabel: Keyboard Instructions, press enter or space to display instructions on how to use the resource window.
resourceMenu.keyboardInstructions:
Use the Skip-To-Question link or F6 to return to the question.

Use the Skip-To-Resources link or F6 on the question to return to the resource.

Use the Minimize button to collapse the Resources window.

Use the Full View button to display the Resources in the full assessment area.

When the Resize button is focused, use the arrow keys to adjust the window size.

When the Close button is focused use the arrow keys to move the Resources window.
